---
import CvLayout from '../layouts/CvLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<CvLayout
  seo={{
    title: 'HEC et après?',
    description: 'Conference "HEC et Après? Le monde des ONGs" at the University of Lausanne. Presentation on Entrepreneurship and NGOs.'
  }}
  breadcrumb="HEC et après?"
>
  <div class="cv-box cv-box--subpage">
    <div class="cv-subpage-header">
      <div class="cv-subpage-category"><Icon name="ph:tag" class="cv-subpage-category__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Conferences</div>
      <h1 class="cv-subpage-title">HEC et après?</h1>
      <div class="cv-subpage-meta">
        <p><Icon name="ph:map-pin" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> University of Lausanne, Switzerland</p>
        <p><Icon name="ph:calendar" class="cv-subpage-meta__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> March 15, 2017</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-content">
      <p>"HEC et Apres? Le monde des ONGs" was a conference organized by an association from the University of Lausanne aimed at informing students about career opportunities in non-profit organizations. Thomas Rouaud was invited as a guest speaker to deliver a lecture on "Entrepreneurship and NGOs."</p>

      <div class="cv-subpage-images">
        <img src="/images/hec-et-apres-1.jpg" alt="Thomas Rouaud speaking at HEC et après conference" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/images/hec-et-apres-2.jpg" alt="Presentation at HEC Lausanne" width="600" height="400" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cv-subpage-footer">
      <a href="/" class="cv-subpage-back"><Icon name="ph:arrow-left" class="cv-subpage-back__icon" aria-hidden="true" /> Retour à la page d'accueil</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</CvLayout>
